b970500 branches
39fcaae use UI

"
 IF WE USE GRAPH, WE CAN SEE WE ARE IN LINEAR MOOD
 MAIN IS NOT DIVERGE FROM BUGFIX BRANCH
"

* 7c4a76d (bugfix/signup-form) fix bug   //in graph mood
* 66580ec (HEAD ->main) create branch    //we just have some forward commits!
* 0af669d create branch
* b970500 branches
* 39fcaae use UI

if we want to bring bugfix changes to main branch,
we just need move main pointer to some forward commits,
it's remain linear, there is not any diverge, history is not changed!
this is FAST "FORWARD MERGE"

"git merge bugfix/signup-form"      //run this on main branch
                                    //to move main to last commit on bugfix branch

* 7c4a76d (HEAD ->main,bugfix/signup-form) fix bug   //after merging
* 66580ec  create branch                             //main &  bugfix will point to 7c4a76d
* 0af669d create branch
* b970500 branches
* 39fcaae use UI

Note: we don't create any new commit
      by merging process!
      so we don't need any new message on merging!

